        {
            "id": "https://www.sakurday.top/minecraftru-he-lian-ji.html",
            "url": "https://www.sakurday.top/minecraftru-he-lian-ji.html",
            "title": "Minecraft如何联机",
            "summary": "mc怎么联机，这个问题曾困扰了古今中外无数科学家。许多人认为这是不可能完成的任务，有人说只有上帝才知道如何联机。在2026年的今天，这个问题依旧是神秘的世界未解之谜之一，引的无数人拼尽全力也要探寻问题的答案。&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">mc怎么联机，这个问题曾困扰了古今中外无数科学家。许多人认为这是不可能完成的任务，有人说只有上帝才知道如何联机。在2026年的今天，这个问题依旧是神秘的世界未解之谜之一，引的无数人拼尽全力也要探寻问题的答案。</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>首先确保你和你的朋友游戏版本完全相同。如果加了模组，请保证你和朋友的模组完全相同。如果加了整合包，请保证你和朋友的整合包完全相同。</p>\n<p>联机有很多方法，但是大多数方法稳定性欠佳或者要求较高。这里我用相对来说比较稳定而且操作难度小的方法——frp（你不需要了解这是什么，照着做就行了）</p>\n<h1>第一步：注册SakuraFrp账号</h1>\n<p>打开<a href=\"https://www.natfrp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">樱花映射</a>。如果你没有注册账号，请注册一个账号。如果注册完毕，打开管理面板</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-16-31.png\" alt=\"打开管理面板\" width=\"1051\" height=\"644\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-16-31-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-16-31-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-16-31-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-16-31-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-16-31-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-16-31-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>樱花映射可以免费用，如果你不交钱，你需要签到获取流量。mc联机传输的所有数据都会消耗这个流量。一般来说一天签到的流量完全够联机了。</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-19-11.png\" alt=\"签到\" width=\"527\" height=\"276\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-19-11-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-19-11-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-19-11-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-19-11-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-19-11-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-19-11-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h1>第二步：下载并登录软件</h1>\n<p>接下来我们下载软件，如图所示：</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-20-03.png\" alt=\"下载软件1\" width=\"454\" height=\"323\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-20-03-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-20-03-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-20-03-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-20-03-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-20-03-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-20-03-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-21-17.png\" alt=\"下载软件2\" width=\"1743\" height=\"494\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-21-17-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-21-17-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-21-17-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-21-17-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-21-17-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-21-17-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>然后打开安装包安装即可。安装完毕后，电脑的开始菜单应该会出现“SakuraFrp 启动器”文件夹，我们点进去打开“SakuraFrp启动器”</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-23-39.png\" alt=\"开始菜单\" width=\"800\" height=\"418\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-23-39-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-23-39-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-23-39-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-23-39-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-23-39-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-23-39-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>打开软件，进入设置，填写密钥，如图所示：</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-25-54.png\" alt=\"密钥\" width=\"1472\" height=\"1086\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-25-54-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-25-54-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-25-54-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-25-54-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-25-54-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-25-54-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>密钥填写后登录，如果登录成功，就可以进行下一步了。</p>\n<h1>第三步：创建隧道</h1>\n<p>进入隧道选项卡，点击加号</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-03.png\" alt=\"创建1\" width=\"1185\" height=\"763\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-03-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-03-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-03-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-03-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-03-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-03-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>在这个界面，我们选一个地理位置离你比较近的（举个例子，如果你在安徽宣城，你应该选择合肥）</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-55.png\" alt=\"选择位置\" width=\"1298\" height=\"887\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-55-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-55-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-55-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-55-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-55-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-28-55-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>接下来会进入更详细的设置，照着图片填，然后直接点创建就好了。</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-34-07.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1298\" height=\"1029\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-34-07-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-34-07-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-34-07-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-34-07-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-34-07-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-34-07-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>然后，隧道列表应该会出现你刚刚创建的隧道了</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-35-19.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1185\" height=\"763\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-35-19-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-35-19-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-35-19-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-35-19-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-35-19-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-35-19-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h1>第四步：打开mc进行愉快的游玩</h1>\n<p>进入你想联机的单人游戏存档，按照图示操作：</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-37-43.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1044\" height=\"661\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-37-43-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-37-43-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-37-43-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-37-43-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-37-43-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-37-43-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-38-20-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1044\" height=\"661\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-38-20-2-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-38-20-2-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-38-20-2-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-38-20-2-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-38-20-2-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-38-20-2-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>创建成功后，我们回到SakuraFrp的软件，开启你刚刚创建的那个隧道。</p>\n<p>然后，进入日志，会发现日志给了我们1-2个ip地址，就是有下划线的部分：</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-40-34.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1185\" height=\"763\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-40-34-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-40-34-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-40-34-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-40-34-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-40-34-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/Snipaste_2026-03-26_21-40-34-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>点击即可复制此ip地址，现在发给你的好友，要你的好友在多人游戏添加服务器，输入这个ip地址，然后愉快的游玩吧！</p>\n<h1>注意事项</h1>\n<p>以下情况需要你另外下载模组：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>你的mc版本比较老，游戏里创建局域网的时候不能自己填端口号</li>\n<li>你的朋友没有正版</li>\n</ol>\n<p>如果出现这种情况，请下载以下模组：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果你的游戏版本小于1.21.4,下载模组 Lan Server Properties</li>\n<li>如果你的游戏版本在1.21.5-1.21.11,下载模组 LAN World Plug-n-Play</li>\n</ul>\n<p>以上模组只需要房主安装即可。安装后，你可以允许没买正版的玩家进来，端口号也可以强制设置为25565了。</p>\n<p>你应该会安装模组的，对吧...</p>\n<h1>和你的朋友愉快的玩耍吧！</h1>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/bdcf2f175dd5caf60341e4b316c0f938.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"512\" height=\"480\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/bdcf2f175dd5caf60341e4b316c0f938-xs.png 640w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/bdcf2f175dd5caf60341e4b316c0f938-sm.png 768w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/bdcf2f175dd5caf60341e4b316c0f938-md.png 1024w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/bdcf2f175dd5caf60341e4b316c0f938-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/bdcf2f175dd5caf60341e4b316c0f938-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.sakurday.top/media/posts/2/responsive/bdcf2f175dd5caf60341e4b316c0f938-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>",
            "author": {
                "name": "Sakurday"
